The civil marriage of the Prince of Naples - who became Victor Emmanuel III

GIA4732914 The civil marriage of the Prince of Naples - who became Victor Emmanuel III (Victor Emmanuel) (Vittorio Emanuele) - with Princess Helene of Montenegro at the Quirinal Palace in 1896. In the center you can see Humbert I (Umberto) on the left of the bride. by Unknown Artist, (19th century); Private Collection; (add.info.: The civil marriage of the Prince of Naples - who became Victor Emmanuel III (Victor Emmanuel) (Vittorio Emanuele) - with Princess Helene of Montenegro at the Quirinal Palace in 1896.
